"emphasize audio on some channels. This is doen by lowering the volume of non-"
"emphasized channels when a emphasized channel is playing, and returning the "
"volumes to normal when no emphasized chanels are playing. By setting this "
"variable to ``[ 'voice' ]``, the voice channel can be emphasized over music "
"and other sounds,"
msgstr ""

