#: ../../source/changelog.rst:4274
msgid ""
"Add the :func:`AlphaBlend` displayable and the :func:`AlphaDissolve` "
"transition. These take two displayables, and use the alpha channel of a "
"third displayable to blend them together. (The third displayable is often an "
"animation, allowing the effect to change over time.)"
