#: ../../source/changelog.rst:4283
msgid ""
"Imagemaps created using the screen language now only have a size equal to "
"that of their ground image. (Previously, they took up the entire screen.) "
"This change makes it easier to position an imagemap at a different location "
"on screen, such as the bottom."
